Our team @teamzrp drove almost 3000 miles round trip to take on the competition at this years @crandonoffroad @ultra4usa race in the #bighouse Jason was on the redemption tour after a couple mechanical issues knocked him out in 2022 and Travis was looking to improve on past finishes here. Our team took on 6 races and pulled down 4 podium’s with 3 3rd 🥉 place finishes and 1 1st 🥇 in the premier #utv Pro Mod ultra4 class. Not to shabby for a couple of hillbillies from #Utah big thanks to our team and all the hard work they put in to make us successful. We couldn’t do it without our partners and sponsors who support our efforts. One thing is certain we are looking forward to next year. #itswhatwedo #madeintheusa #billet #raceproven #onlythebest #lighterfasterstronger #teamzrp #zrparmy #gofast #racecarparts #rzr #canam #ridefox #teamfk #builtonbfg #redemption #crandon #wisconsin #getitricky #slayersgonnaslay #cantstopus #team #ultra4 #ultra4racing #ultra4usa 📸 @harlenfoley #zrplife
